      <data key="d6">SPEAKER_02</data>
      <data key="d10">SPEAKER_02 opens as meeting host and hands over to John — consistent with a Kumulus sales facilitator role. Confidence lowered from 0.9 because SPEAKER_02 identity is inferred from role, not a name quote.</data>
      <data key="d7">["chapter:01", "chapter:12"]</data>
      <data key="d9">[{"quote": "Brendan Hughes, Laura Gongas, Mediha Zukic, Deon Kuhn, Namrata Tanwani, Vanessa Patrocinio, Momoko Iwagami, João (John) Marçura", "ts": 2, "source": "frames:frame-00001.png"}, {"quote": "Perfect. So thank you so much for your time for joining us today. Today, John will walk you through the proposal.", "ts": 2, "source": "transcript"}, {"quote": "kumulus | John Marcura Bio Gyrus MedBrief | Vanessa Patrocinio | Steve Ashford | Brendan H | Mediha Zukic | Lucas Oliveira", "ts": 3669, "source": "frames"}]</data>
