      <data key="d6">SPEAKER_00</data>
      <data key="d10">Joao addresses SPEAKER_00 as 'Brandon' (transcription variant); name confirmed as Brendan Hughes from participant grid. Also labelled 'Brandon Hughes' in group-04.</data>
      <data key="d7">["chapter:03", "chapter:04", "chapter:06", "chapter:10", "chapter:12"]</data>
      <data key="d9">[{"quote": "Go on, Brandon.", "ts": 342, "source": "transcript"}, {"quote": "Can I add on this? Can I just make sure that we're talking in the same language here", "ts": 138, "source": "transcript"}, {"quote": "Brendan Hughes, Laura Gongas, Mediha Zukic, Deon Kuhn, Namrata Tanwani, Vanessa Patrocinio, Momoko Iwagami, João (John) Marçura", "ts": 2, "source": "frames:frame-00001.png"}, {"quote": "I just wanted to understand whether you would be using a particular classification schema for the entities once they've been identified, or could we consult with you around the first layers of that classification schema.", "ts": 1345, "source": "transcript"}, {"quote": "we were looking outside because we thought it was sponsored, to be direct about that.", "ts": 3496, "source": "transcript"}]</data>
    </node>
