      <data key="d10">Confirmed as SPEAKER_01 per speaker mapping; challenged NICE historical API claim.</data>
      <data key="d7">["chapter:03", "chapter:04", "chapter:05"]</data>
      <data key="d9">[{"quote": "probably Steve, are you around? Steve would be the person to...", "ts": 123, "source": "transcript"}, {"quote": "I probably say, normally, no, no. It's one, but you can quite often be two or three.", "ts": 125, "source": "transcript"}, {"quote": "kumulus | John Marcura Bio Gyrus MedBrief | Vanessa Patrocinio | Steve Ashford | Brendan H | Mediha Zukic | Lucas Oliveira", "ts": 3669, "source": "frames:frame-00018.png"}, {"quote": "about two years ago I asked them whether we could get old versions of guidelines and they said the only way to get them was to go to the National Archive.", "ts": 960, "source": "transcript"}]</data>
