      <data key="d9">[{"quote": "Brendan Hughes, Laura Gongas, Mediha Zukic, Deon Kuhn, Namrata Tanwani, Vanessa Patrocinio, Momoko Iwagami, João (John) Marçura", "ts": 2, "source": "frames:frame-00001.png"}, {"quote": "We had someone who was manually checking if we missed a certain of in that document or if we over... a pseudonymized or not, manually visually checking, because obviously all the PDFs that you can detect by text is a pseudonymized, but something that somehow maybe OCR or handwritten parts didn't OCR correctly. That's the part that we were missing.", "ts": 2235, "source": "transcript"}]</data>
