    <node id="visual:0005">
      <data key="d0">VisualContext</data>
      <data key="d1">Current Environment &amp; Pain Points</data>
      <data key="d2">0.9</data>
      <data key="d9">[{"quote": "CURRENT ENVIRONMENT &amp; PAIN POINTS\nMedbrief is building a platform to support medical-legal case intelligence by comparing patient case documentation against NICE medical guidelines. Today, this is a highly manual process involving legal and clinical review of large volumes of PDF documentation, requiring complex interpretation and evidence review.\nKEY CHALLENGES\nLarge volumes of unstructured medical-legal PDF documentation.\nManual comparison between case documentation and NICE guidelines.\nNeed to identify correct historical NICE versions based on case dates.\nSensitive medical and personal information risks.\nEntity ambiguity across patients, doctors, hospitals, and documents.\nOCR limitations and inconsistent document quality.\nNeed for explainable, auditable, and defensible outputs.", "ts": 42.0, "source": "vision"}]</data>
      <data key="d7">["chapter:01"]</data>
      <data key="d37">frame-00006.png</data>
      <data key="d28">42.0</data>
      <data key="d38">slide</data>
      <data key="d39">CURRENT ENVIRONMENT &amp; PAIN POINTS
Medbrief is building a platform to support medical-legal case intelligence by comparing patient case documentation against NICE medical guidelines. Today, this is a highly manual process involving legal and clinical review of large volumes of PDF documentation, requiring complex interpretation and evidence review.
KEY CHALLENGES
Large volumes of unstructured medical-legal PDF documentation.
Manual comparison between case documentation and NICE guidelines.
Need to identify correct historical NICE versions based on case dates.
Sensitive medical and personal information risks.
Entity ambiguity across patients, doctors, hospitals, and documents.
OCR limitations and inconsistent document quality.
Need for explainable, auditable, and defensible outputs.</data>
      <data key="d29">A Kumulus slide listing Medbrief's current challenges: large volumes of unstructured medical-legal PDFs, manual comparison against NICE guidelines, OCR limitations, entity ambiguity, and sensitive data risks. This slide frames the problem Kumulus is proposing to solve.</data>
      <data key="d40">2cd4dcd4d45c800c</data>
    </node>
