      <data key="d9">[{"quote": "ENGAGEMENT SCOPE\nPoV Focus: Feasibility of for one surgery case selected by Medbrief, NICE guideline ingestion, extracting/pseudonymizing sensitive entities, and case-guideline comparison.\nIN SCOPE\nOne medical domain: ex. hernia surgery.\nOne current and one 2020 NICE guideline version.\nOne or two real case examples.\nExisting OCR using Document Intelligence.\nEntity extraction and identity resolution.\nDeterministic pseudonymization.\nInitial case vs guideline comparison.\nEvidence-backed outputs for review.\nOUT OF SCOPE\nHandwritten medical notes.\nFull historical NICE processing.\nFull production application development.\nGraphQL or custom API layer development.\nDICOM and radiology processing.", "ts": 293.286, "source": "vision"}]</data>
