      <data key="d29">Linear data flow diagram showing five stages: Sources (NICE API, Case PDFs, OCR Output) through Orchestration (Data Factory), Processing (Databricks entity resolution and pseudonymisation), Engine (case vs guideline comparison and AI reasoning), to Outcome (evidence-backed explainable output). Security First and Traceability notes are highlighted. Presenter is Joao (John) Margura.</data>
