    <node id="visual:0021">
      <data key="d0">VisualContext</data>
      <data key="d1">Assumptions and Limits 1/2</data>
      <data key="d2">0.9</data>
      <data key="d9">[{"quote": "ASSUMPTIONS AND LIMITS 1/2\n\nPOV SCOPE\n• Limited to one selected medical domain category.\n• One current and one 2020 historical NICE version.\n• Process up to two selected surgery cases of the same medical domain.\n• Validate technical feasibility, not production-ready.\n\nCASE DATA SCOPE\n• Digitalised, OCR-readable documents only.\n• Handwritten notes and low-quality scans are Out of Scope.\n• DICOM and radiology imaging are Out of Scope.\n\nNICE API SCOPE\n• Medbrief leads access, credentials, and licensing.\n• Kumulus supports technical validation of access.\n• Access delays may impact timeline or scope.\n• Full catalog ingestion is Out of Scope.", "ts": 3245.0, "source": "vision"}]</data>
      <data key="d7">["chapter:11"]</data>
      <data key="d37">chapframe-11.png</data>
      <data key="d28">3245.0</data>
      <data key="d38">slide</data>
      <data key="d39">ASSUMPTIONS AND LIMITS 1/2

POV SCOPE
• Limited to one selected medical domain category.
• One current and one 2020 historical NICE version.
• Process up to two selected surgery cases of the same medical domain.
• Validate technical feasibility, not production-ready.

CASE DATA SCOPE
• Digitalised, OCR-readable documents only.
• Handwritten notes and low-quality scans are Out of Scope.
• DICOM and radiology imaging are Out of Scope.

NICE API SCOPE
• Medbrief leads access, credentials, and licensing.
• Kumulus supports technical validation of access.
• Access delays may impact timeline or scope.
• Full catalog ingestion is Out of Scope.</data>
      <data key="d29">Slide outlining POV scope (one medical domain, up to two surgery cases, technical feasibility only), Case Data Scope (digitalised OCR-readable documents only; handwritten notes and DICOM out of scope), and NICE API Scope (Medbrief leads access and licensing; full catalogue ingestion out of scope). Critical for understanding what is and is not included in the proposal. Presenter is Joao (John) Margura.</data>
      <data key="d40">ba283434743c0004</data>
    </node>
    <edge source="person:joao-margura" target="chapter:01" id="e-0002">
      <data key="d41">OCCURS_IN</data>
      <data key="d42">person:joao-margura</data>
