      <data key="d44">0.9</data>
      <data key="d45">[{"quote": "we already talked about, for example, Microsoft Fabric, but I don't think it's the best way, and just why when you are going to scale this in production, you will need to have parallel processing and Databricks is the best to win the market for doing parallel processing using Spark", "ts": 1985, "source": "transcript"}]</data>
