      <data key="d45">[{"quote": "Kickoff &amp; Alignment — Confirm goals, stakeholders, case documents, and NICE category. Environment Readiness — Weeks 1-2 — Prepare Data Factory, Databricks, and storage structure. NICE Integration — Weeks 3-5 — Validate API feasibility and review guideline content. Case Data Processing — Weeks 5-7 — Process PDFs via OCR, load, clean, and preserve metadata. Entity &amp; Pseudonymisation — Weeks 7-8 — Extract patients, resolve identities, and apply pseudonyms. Comparison &amp; Findings — Weeks 8-10 — Structure logic, generate results, and present final summary.", "ts": 2879, "source": "frames"}, {"quote": "we divided these in six steps, as I already showed to you. The last one being the handover, and step 5 being the real comparison.", "ts": 2629, "source": "transcript"}]</data>
    </edge>
