      <data key="d44">0.85</data>
      <data key="d45">[{"quote": "Even when using Azure Foundry models, it's too risky. We don't want to share PII information that's a breach of compliance. So what we are planning is identifying all the PII before... and then doing the redaction.", "ts": 1330, "source": "transcript"}]</data>
