      <data key="d45">[{"quote": "Microsoft funding is related to timing of completion of the project. So if we block on some milestone or we delay a lot the project, we are at a high risk of losing the Microsoft incentives. I think it's 12 weeks is the maximum time that Microsoft gives to deliver a POV solution.", "ts": 2739, "source": "transcript"}, {"quote": "I suggest we select, you know, kind of a simple case and does not have like... Dozens of guidelines, because we really want to streamline the whole process and make sure it works before we start expanding", "ts": 430, "source": "transcript"}]</data>
